reviews.title: QR code scanning? Kidding?
reviews.comment: Then don\'t wonder why the bank is the worst in ranking of Internet services.  I\'m really interested to see the person who came up with the idea of QR code scanning for invoices. How many have you seen in your life with QR?  Every bank from ages ago scans ocr and amount and Nordea came up with the idea of how to prove that for real we are the worst when it comes to Internet services.  You are lucky a lot of your customers have not worked with other bank apps and their functions and simple scanning systems.
reviews.author: Farshin H

Danske bank har l\303\244nge haft en innovativ app. L\303\244r av era konkurrenter och kom ifatt annars kommer ni s\303\244kerligen b\303\266rja f\303\266rlora kunder.
